tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE algorithm_runs (
    run_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    algorithm_id INT,
    start_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    end_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    FOREIGN KEY (algorithm_id) REFERENCES quantum_algorithm_performance_metrics(algorithm_id)
);

CREATE TABLE AlgorithmResults (
    result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    algorithm_id INT,
    success BOOLEAN,
    result_data TEXT,
    FOREIGN KEY (algorithm_id) REFERENCES QuantumAlgorithmMetrics(algorithm_id)
);

CREATE TABLE AlgorithmTagRelations (
    relation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    algorithm_id INT,
    tag_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (algorithm_id) REFERENCES QuantumAlgorithmMetrics(algorithm_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (tag_id) REFERENCES AlgorithmTags(tag_id)
);
